We have made some improvements to the Search view: You can now sort songs by popularity trending recently added song name artist name or duration Search history shows you your most recent searches. You can clear your search history by tapping on Clear recent searches at the end of the list. The update also includes general bug fixes and improvements. If you experience any issues with Singa please send an email to support singa.com and we ll get back to you as soon as possible.

We ve streamlined the singing flow to get you singing more intuitively. The karaoke player now has a settings icon on the top left corner giving access to song versions and song version settings. You can now adjust pitch in real time from the top of the player control view. Long press a song in the Discover view to add it to favourites on a singlist or in the queue. If you experience any issues with Singa please send an email to support singa.com and we ll get back to you as soon as possible.

We ve made a complete rewrite of the app to make your experience better. These under the hood changes will make the app run better faster and stronger. Changes: We have added new Me icon to the bottom navigation bar so that you can access your profile favorites song history and singlists more easily. Support for iOS 10 was removed so you can have the latest and shiniest features! If you experience any issues with Singa please send an email to support singa.com and we ll get back to you as soon as possible.

Guys and gals this is a maintenance update! We re rushing full steam ahead with Singster trying to make it better each day and well... sometimes mistakes happen : This update brings a lot of stability to the app such as: Update: All network related tasks are now way faster than before lighting speed! Update: We ll remember and be able to detect you better when you sign in Update: Once you sing a song you ll be able to sing it again without having to wait for the download to start Fix: Long songs might have crashed the app for some users that shouldn t happen anymore Fix: If you want to stop the song before it s end you ll now come straight back to where you started Fix: Overall improved stability May not be true: this app was Born to Be Wild and will Fight For Your Right To Party .

This is it! The past few weeks we ve been hard at work trying to make Singster better each day and now we are proud to say that this update brings on some very anticipated updates: New: New songs coming each week maybe even each day if we re lucky! You can share your own videos and others cool videos to Email SMS Facebook Twitter and many other social networks Recorded videos are now DOUBLE as sharp than before Fixed: A lot of general improvements Performance updates especially for iPhone 4 and 4S Easier to write a description for your video Pushing stop while a song was loading crashed the app for some user now it shouldn t You can now see your face! No more Stop buttons blocking the view when watching videos May not be true: This app is the secret love child of Mozart and Madonna

Like we promised on our last update there s still PLENTY of things to fix and add: New: You can now send invitations to friends with email to get up to five free weeks of Singster New: Subscription management in Settings view. Check your Me tab and click the upper left corner for Settings New: Profile view functionality and navigation updated. Fixed: Delay non sync between audio video in recorded performances for some users Fixed: App doesn t auto lock now when you don t touch the screen for a longer time Fixed: Tapping song item in Activity now opens the song in question Fixed: Activity search bar isn t as prone to wrong clicks as it was before Fixed: Generally a lot of other improvements..a lot. May not be true: This app has won many prestigious singing competitions such as the Eurovision Song Contest The Voice and X Factor.

Fixed: Facebook authentication crash for some users New: A LOT of general improvements more to come! May not be true: If you use Singster in the shower you will almost certainly sound like Barry White and or Celine Dion.
